
Charles Bisesto is a Political Science and Sociology doublemajor from San Francisco. He was LEAD ASUCD Senate senatorial candidate in the Fall 2006 ASUCD Election, but his bid was unsuccessful. Charles is a former President of Sigma Chi, captain of the UC Davis Crew Team, a member of the Davis Honors Challenge and an employee at Campus Copies/Classical Notes. He also participated in the UCDC program where he interned for US Senator Diane Feinstein. Charles was also an intern for San Francisco mayor Gavin Newsom as well the Democratic National Committee during the 2004 Presidential elections.
